comment0.text=\r\n\ AUTHOR\:\ danpost\ (greenfoot.org\ username)<br>\r\n\ VERSION\:\ 1.0<br>\r\n\ LAST\ MODIFIED\:\ November\ 5,\ 2012<br>\r\n\ <br>\r\n\ DESCRIPTION\:<br>\r\n\ a\ subclass\ of\ the\ Bar\ class\ that\ gives\ the\ bar\ user\ click\ functionality,\r\n\ and\ sets\ a\ public\ boolean\ to\ true\ to\ inform\ the\ world\ of\ any\ value\ changes.\r\n\ This\ variable\ must\ be\ reset\ to\ 'false'\ as\ soon\ as\ it\ is\ found\ to\ be\ 'true'\ in\ the\ world\ class.\r\n
