comment2.text=\r\n\ allows\ the\ user\ to\ perform\ mouse\ presses\ and\ clicks\ on\ (and\ beside)\ the\ bar\ to\ change\ its\ value.\r\n\ The\ following\ four\ places\ can\ be\ clicked\ at\:<br>\r\n\ \ 1)\ Outside,\ to\ left\ of\ color\ bar\:\ minimizes\ value,\ and\ begins\ incrementing\ if\ mouse\ press\ held<br>\r\n\ \ 2)\ Outside,\ to\ right\ of\ color\ bar\:\ maximizes\ value,\ and\ begins\ decrementing\ if\ mouse\ press\ held<br>\r\n\ \ 3)\ Inside,\ on\ left\ side\ of\ color\ bar\:\ decrements\ value,\ and\ decrements\ more\ if\ mouse\ press\ held<br>\r\n\ \ 4)\ Inside,\ on\ right\ side\ of\ color\ bar\:\ increments\ value,\ and\ increments\ more\ if\ mouse\ press\ held<br>\r\n
